name: City Runner 101
description:
PNG 5000 x 5000 px
Made with Processing

The unique rendered output of an algorithm exploring the (non)-intersection of line segments. Every iteration a horizontal or vertical line is drawn without intersecting any of the already existing lines. Over time the available space gets increasingly subdivided. Due to the ghost in the machine there still are a couple of line intersections, (see if you can spot them) making this piece all the more unique.
